# Screen Recordings Directory

Store screen recordings here organized by date:

```
recordings/
├── 2024-11-17/
│   ├── complete-survey-flow-desktop.mp4
│   ├── offline-sync-demo.mp4
│   └── ...
├── 2024-11-18/
│   └── ...
```

## When to Record

- Complex user interactions
- Bugs that are hard to describe with screenshots
- Performance issues
- Complete user flow demonstrations
- Issues that only occur during specific sequences

## Naming Convention

`[description]-[device]-[date].mp4`

Examples:
- `complete-survey-flow-desktop-2024-11-17.mp4`
- `gps-capture-issue-mobile-2024-11-17.mp4`
- `offline-sync-tablet-2024-11-17.mp4`
